metadata.name: Psychedelic Healing
metadata.description: A translucent hand releases a magical pill, radiant with the potential of psychological and spiritual well-being. A second hand reaches for the gift of healing. The rainbow emanation of spheres relates to the infinite potential of psychedelics to awaken 'the spark of life,' and then to pass it on.â €This NFT of the MAPS Logo is based on my painting entitled 'Psychedelic Healing.' Thanks to visionary filmmaker, Matteo Santoro for working with me on the animation and soundtrack.
